            <description><![CDATA[<div class="quote"><blockquote><font size="2"><a href="https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&goto=findpost&pid=48029432&ptid=1944837" target="_blank"><font color="#999999">john 发表于 2020-7-1 23:33</font></a></font><br>
是我看的企业级太低端了吗，这几个数量级在哪里<br>
<br>
SM983</blockquote></div><br>
指标错了, 应该看UBER(Uncorrectable Bit Error Rate), 确实比消费级高一个数量级<br>
<br>
P4510 UBER: 1 sector per 10^17 bits read, 扇区应该是照512Byte计算。<br>
660P UBER: <1 sector per 10^15 bits read<br>
<br>
这种表征纠错容忍度的指标很能体现颗粒本身的素质以及主控的纠错能力。]]></description>
